{"tid":358022,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"出三保有D野唔明","createTime":"2017-08-13T12:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T01:37:40.000Z","uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89b087fb4c05917bc26033e4b5911b43ab32d6e2","tid":358022,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"小弟打算過一排出車, 但有d疑問, 想問下巴打<br />\n我就夠曬25歲+夠2年牌齡(連P)<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果出三保, quote泰x保險個價錢係$1,9xx係咪實價+正常?<br />\n因為我quote快而x個價成四千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者巴打會唔會有咩其他公司介紹?<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果牌薄落自己名, 係咪唔可以搵直屬出三保? <br />\n因為直屬牌齡20幾年, 出三保一定平<br />\n但我同直屬唔係一齊住, 如果租屋村停車場既話牌溥唔係我名(住戶)就應該租唔到<br />\n所以想知係咪牌薄係我, 就一定要自己出三保?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手買車唔識野多多見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1605dbda58447f56e86e6641a10738d3c2e0999","tid":358022,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"你夠歲又夠牌齡<br />\n上網quote 多幾間lor"},{"pid":"336bf6bf21396019df865123067677556ce6fe24","tid":358022,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你夠歲又夠牌齡<br />\n上網quote 多幾間lor</blockquote><br />\n但2千蚊有三保，係唔係正常價？定其實佢仲有其他費用未收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e74462121817ca283417a0a14d0a6dfd0f3d84","tid":358022,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"上網價未必準<br />\n一定要靠正式報價單"},{"pid":"bfcf1862634a0f4d49fb19261bddbe82f8b4a6f9","tid":358022,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"咁平有機係鬼保 同埋好多保險公司係唔計你P嗰一年 所以其實你係得一年駕駛經驗"},{"pi